---
import Container from "../shared/Container.astro";
import Title from "../shared/Title.astro";
---

<section>
  <Container className="space-y-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <Title> About Book World Travel </Title>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 max-md:flex-col max-md:gap-12">
      <div
        class="w-1/3 max-md:w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-black gap-3"
      >
        <img
          class="w-72 aspect-square rounded-full"
          src="/images/about1.webp"
          alt=""
        />
        <div class="text-xl font-semibold">Our Story</div>
        <div class="text-center">
          We started Book World Travel with a simple goal: to help people
          explore the world. Our team of experienced travel experts work
          tirelessly to craft unique and unforgettable experiences for our
          clients.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="w-1/3 max-md:w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-black gap-3"
      >
        <img
          class="w-72 aspect-square rounded-full"
          src="/images/about2.webp"
          alt=""
        />
        <div class="text-xl font-semibold">Our Services</div>
        <div class="text-center">
          At Book World Travel, we offer a wide range of services to make your
          travel experience as smooth and stress-free as possible. From flight
          bookings to hotel reservations, we have got you covered.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="w-1/3 max-md:w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-black gap-3"
      >
        <img
          class="w-72 aspect-square rounded-full"
          src="/images/about3.webp"
          alt=""
        />
        <div class="text-xl font-semibold">Our Destinations</div>
        <div class="text-center">
          With Book World Travel, you can travel to some of the most exotic and
          breathtaking destinations on the planet. Whether you want to explore
          ancient ruins or soak up the sun on a tropical beach, we have a
          destination that's perfect for you.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
